Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.82,Naminanakai Public Hospital,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Naminanakai Public Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:12.02,Episode-Title,episode,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Fourteen: \N The Promised Day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.90,Naminanakai Public Hospital,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Naminanakai Public Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.24,Main,nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chisaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.97,Main,nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Must be hard, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:22.06,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No... my school is nearby, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.24,Kihara Isamu,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara Isamu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:25.23,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There's some left over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:28.20,Main,nurse,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem to have \Nmuch of an appetite lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:33.80,Main,nurse,0000,0000,0000,,You should come here once you're \Ndone with nursing school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:37.89,Main,nurse,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a huge help, having \Nsomeone as reliable as you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:40.30,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.05,South 412,sign,0000,0000,0000,,South 412 \N Yamaguchi Youhei \N Kihara Isamu \NTanaka Masaru \N Kitagawa Kyosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:44.86,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, you have to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.50,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,There's no flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:52.11,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're out of the hospital, you can\Neat whatever you want as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:53.94,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm going to wipe you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.82,Sea Salt,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Salt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.58,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the Tomoebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.36,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoebi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:15.09,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,We all have to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.54,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Someone important's coming, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:24.94,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently a professor \Nfrom Tsumugu's lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.54,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:34.67,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,If he's from the city, he \Nprobably won't like country cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.64,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Go buy some alcohol and meat with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:38.48,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.65,Oshiooshi Station,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Oshiooshi Station Front
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.68,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.48,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Sayama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.78,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about stopping \Nby Saya Mart on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.98,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.42,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Egawa's getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:27.96,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,He knocked a girl up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.77,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,K-Knoc—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.70,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,B-But what about college?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.92,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the girl's dad is \Nthe president of some company,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.01,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,so he's going to quit school \Nand work at her dad's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.46,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.21,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's this year's biggest surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:44.17,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd be back for the \Ncoming-of-age ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.13,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,so we're all gonna tease him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.31,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's changed so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.22,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and it's only been five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.08,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've changed the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:53.73,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.84,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:57.79,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor going around like \Nyou're some lonely housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.69,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,It's oddly hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.69,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.70,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.34,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You were probably out \Nplaying pachinko again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.08,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Just went out for a refresher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.24,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,The boss was waiting \N quite a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.30,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.70,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Akira-kun. This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.28,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.66,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Fanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.20,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:36.82,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He only listens to Miuna so I \Ndon't know what to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:38.60,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.84,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:48.28,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the sea \Ncan hibernate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.28,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then Hikari-kun and the others \Nare probably asleep, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.94,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'm sure they're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:55.05,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.50,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:58.90,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Akari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:04.29,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can have \Nthe baby right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.08,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,We've been blessed with a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.90,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.24,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:12.75,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.99,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Just go over there! Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.25,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.08,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.65,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:33.91,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.68,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,A boy, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.54,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.32,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.02,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy that I'll have a younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:53.15,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:05.17,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.32,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, i-it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.61,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,Kancho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.70,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.10,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.25,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He's so obsessed with that lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.46,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.58,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... you dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.05,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.24,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did you get one of your \Nspecial kancho attacks in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:27.09,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I said, wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.09,Main,saya,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.15,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.23,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-u-na.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.77,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.49,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.49,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.83,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,You look a lot like your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.92,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.10,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Your sleeping face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.86,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari used to sleep a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:02.92,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.13,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Now, today's the day of \Nthe exciting Tomoebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:10.44,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Before, you couldn't see it unless \Nyou were at the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.34,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,And, now it's the moon \Nrather than the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.39,Tomoebi,board,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoebi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:17.54,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Because the sea is frozen, \Nthe ice acts like a prism,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:20.23,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,and gathers the light \Nfrom the saltflake snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:22.54,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,That creates an image in the atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:25.23,Tomoebi Before,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoebi Before\NOnly visible from inside the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:25.23,Temperature,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Temperature \N Water Temperature\N Tidal Current
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:25.23,Sun,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:25.23,Nagi Sea Level,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Calm Sea Surface
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:25.23,Tidal Current,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tidal Current
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.83,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,and makes an illusory moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.44,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,When the moon is low\Nin the sky, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.38,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say 8 o'clock is probably \Nthe best viewing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.75,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:36.32,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Oh, right. Dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.84,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,After this, it's time to get \Nready for the rice feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.44,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Having a rice feeding by \Nthe sea with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.44,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hello, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.88,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of nostalgic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.88,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The main event is the Tomoebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:45.95,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:46.88,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.42,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Having class at night is exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.18,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Minegishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:53.09,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.89,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Be on your guard, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.34,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.37,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I totally found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:05.61,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,When the Tomoebi happens
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.65,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Minegishi's planning to ask you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:09.86,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.87,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:15.13,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,School's a place for studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.74,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu, you used to hate studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:23.00,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that I'm going \Nto be a girl living on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.51,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm going to \Nfind work in Oshiooshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:29.63,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to go out into the city \Nand become an independent woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.51,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You've thought out your future that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.69,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. What about you, Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.81,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.64,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't plan on leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.40,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.22,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.31,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:56.35,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair's gotten longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.00,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.38,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.16,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher's calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.35,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:06.66,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.91,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.75,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you guys have to be in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:18.02,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I always watched from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.89,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.25,Flashback,blah,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:21.81,Flashback,blah,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:22.30,Flashback,tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Mukaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.89,Flashback,blah,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The bridge pier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:25.30,Flashback,scream,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.90,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I \Ndecided I wouldn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:35.58,Italics,iuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because I knew that Hikari and \Nthe others were in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:38.51,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that they were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:45.36,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari and the others are still \Nsomewhere I can't go, smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:47.69,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.37,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.57,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.22,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:55.95,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's my turn today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:00.17,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:02.78,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I went to look at the \Nsea again for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:05.23,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,But something's in the \Nway so it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.56,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,The sea temperature's gone down, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.11,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Is your tummy okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.54,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:15.23,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,We'd always gotten pregnant \Nand raised our young in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.42,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.20,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.46,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He's not alone... Dad's there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:30.21,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,And Hikari liked Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:35.55,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,If Manaka and the others had been \Nleft in the sea, and he was alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:38.72,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Hikari \Nwould know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:41.60,Flashback-Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari... likes Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.65,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miuna. It'll spill over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.47,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.82,Flashback-Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,He likes Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.37,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:54.39,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.36,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:01.82,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I look out from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:08.08,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,To the sea where Hikari \Nand the others are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:28.21,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Professor! Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:33.17,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Why not warm up a little \Nbefore the Tomoebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.31,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.43,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,The stewed golden-eye is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:43.20,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get food \Nlike this in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.01,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:45.97,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:48.79,Main,Chisa,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing. As long as you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.58,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The meat is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.80,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to barge in like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:56.83,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.46,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It's lively, and I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.12,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Because Tsumugu came to our lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.09,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,our research has progressed quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.48,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,There are only fourteen \Nsea villages in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:12.60,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, we can't step \Nfoot into any of them right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.62,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we try diving to investigate,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.80,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,the tide gets in our way and we \Ncan't get close to the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:23.04,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,There are even specialists now saying \Nthat the sea villages don't exist anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.89,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,They're just saying \Nthat to get attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.60,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Hiradaira-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:35.12,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that there is a close relationship \Nbetween the surface and the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.64,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,To explain the abnormal weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:40.06,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,we need to research the \Nsea villages as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:42.26,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:45.31,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll bring you another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.97,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.87,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,She's a great girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.65,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure there's nothing going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.76,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:14:00.06,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are at that age and \Nyou're living under one roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.98,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, she's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.86,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,that'd usually mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:07.23,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,She has someone else that \Nshe's liked for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.06,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.45,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:19.66,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,He can take care of the futon himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:21.42,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,He's a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.46,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:26.82,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you come see the Tomoebi, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.22,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:33.22,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in seeing the \NTomoebi without the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.33,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to make some \Namazake since it's cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.73,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.24,Flashback,boys,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.74,Flashback,boys,0000,0000,0000,,It really did turn into a huge deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.14,Flashback,adult,0000,0000,0000,,Did we find the sea \Nkids that fell in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.98,Flashback,adult,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time something \Nlike this ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.21,Flashback,adult,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the Sea \NGod was this angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.10,Flashback,adult,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.66,Flashback,adult,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have any \Nrelatives on the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:05.79,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.21,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome in our home...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.67,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,You can come live with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.05,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:13.63,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,You've already got a full \Nhouse in your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:15.10,Flashback,gramp,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.10,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the sea, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.81,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, the lady next door \Nwanted to give this to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.21,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Grandp—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.25,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.13,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wake up! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.63,In Surgery,sign,0000,0000,0000,,In Surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.13,Flashback,nurse,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a family member, \Nplease wait over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.64,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't take Grandpa away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.75,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.14,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:44.58,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take anyone else away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.42,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:45.58,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.42,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Did you pack your underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:57.07,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:00.96,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You're not all there when \Nit comes to stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:06.32,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna be a college \Nstudent in the big city...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.45,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oceanography researcher \Nis really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:10.73,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You should be proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:15.36,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that you somehow ended \Nup taking care of Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:19.41,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is my other family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.56,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,My precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.50,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Family, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.85,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do research in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.01,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,About the sea villages,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.18,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,about what happened that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:36.57,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're tied into what's \Ngoing to happen on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.00,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.80,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.46,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If everything takes a \Nturn for the better,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:46.20,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.35,Flashback,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.23,Main,student,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.38,Main,student,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Mine is all potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.23,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:09.61,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,The Tomoebi is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.44,Main,boy a,0000,0000,0000,,Minegishi, what about Shiodome?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.37,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:14.67,Main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.24,Main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day you prove you're a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.03,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, boys are so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.03,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Your tray. I'll go put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.24,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.40,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The currents...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.71,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.00,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.69,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Since that day, the sea has been calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.30,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly... Quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:48.85,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Not telling me what's \Nhappening below.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.16,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,Shiodome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:57.03,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.78,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... asking me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.71,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Wh-Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:05.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I was being \Noverly self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.18,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm wrong, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.04,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,You're not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:11.10,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me say this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.63,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.67,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.88,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,So... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:19.68,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.89,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked you! \NEver since grade school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.65,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.80,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.29,Main,mina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.33,Main,mina,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this guy you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.78,Main,mina,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.26,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.36,Main,mine,0000,0000,0000,,Shiodome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.04,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Tomoebi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.93,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite magnificent, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.07,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.45,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Something big is showing up on screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.44,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:23.82,Main,prof,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.58,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.60,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:00.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed at all \Nfrom back then... not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:04.51,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,He's not breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:11.81,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't think doing mouth-to-mouth \Non a person from the sea will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hika—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.31,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,She's Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.58,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.79,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.81,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,had stopped moving in sadness.
